     <ul>
       <li>
        Phone consultation: No charge​
         </li>
        <li>
        Diagnosis – $50 for 1 hour minimum<br>
         </li>
       <li>
        Amp testing, research problem
        If I repair the amp in the same hour, $50 fee applies.<br>

        If along the way I discover a repair is much more complex than anticipated, I stop and return the amp, no fee.​
         </li>
                <li> Basic Easy Fix - $50 for 1 hour minimum, $15 per quarter hour after that.</li>
  
        <li>To book an appointment, shoot me an email with information about your amp, and the issue(s) you are experiencing. Note, it can take a few days for me to respond.
</li>

