    <article class="identity">
      <h2>Ecology</h2>
      <p>
        Any electronic components or systems, manufactured before 2006, will most likely contain lead solder and other hazardous substances. Repairing or restoring broken gear will help keep electronic waste from ending up in the landfill while also not requiring new resorces to be used to produce your sound.
      </p>
